{"tid":1984113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾乎日日都確診輸入個案，唔喺源頭阻截？？","createTime":"2020-04-22T08:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T07:30:29.000Z","uid":92979,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"487d7fc536fb958164f1dd15fbfd869caa1c70b2","tid":1984113,"uid":92979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"最近呢一個星期嘅確診者，極大部份都有外遊紀錄或者外國返嚟，係咪因為佢哋嘅自由乜乜能，搞到一直冇辦法 0 確診。佢哋嘅自由，就要全港人日日外出都要戴口罩，消費活動又種種限制，咁樣真係冇問題？？"},{"pid":"f92b701ccd6383a3b4258c341edaaaa5798148e3","tid":1984113,"uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔通唔俾人返黎香港？<br />\n而家非香港人入唔到境"},{"pid":"c589ea5287590f1924854b14a26be7d003b5b98f","tid":1984113,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f92b701ccd6383a3b4258c341edaaaa5798148e3","tid":1984113,"uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔通唔俾人返黎香港？<br />\n而家非香港人入唔到境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b13d4f64dcd283147a065e0bb96071c7131416","tid":1984113,"uid":92979,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f92b701ccd6383a3b4258c341edaaaa5798148e3","tid":1984113,"uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"唔通唔俾人返黎香港？<br />\n而家非香港人入唔到境"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"就係因為呢種講法<br />\n<br />\n所以幾乎日日都有呢類新增<br />\n<br />\n而個後果要全部香港人承受<br />\n<br />\n即係香港人日日好乖咁做足防疫措施<br />\n<br />\n但因為嗰班人，搞到冇得停？？<br />\n<br />\n各行各業都搞咁多野防疫，喺香港生存生活嘅人，就要不斷為佢哋埋單？？"},{"pid":"8e27962e9fedfc9cf4d7798082655f691a0a25cf","tid":1984113,"uid":7610,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"咁唔係點？<br />\n唔通唔俾香港人返嚟香港？"},{"pid":"dd848a1d353d57a8c15b1441029dbc5aea86065f","tid":1984113,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8b13d4f64dcd283147a065e0bb9